content: Unbeknownst to many, the royal Lunarian family has a secret jewel-cutting technique that can maintain the power of large moonstones while shrinking down to a manageable size, granting them the unique ability to carry a powerful refined moonstone in the palm of their hand.
title: Refined Moonstone #1

content: The most prized of Lunarian cultural artifacts are so-called "perfect" moonstones. Each is painstakingly researched, carefully handled, and meticulously crafted to form the pinnacle of wealth and status in Lunarian society. Ownership of one denotes incredible wealth and power.
title: Perfect Moonstone #1

content: Occasionally a small shard of moonstone is tossed aside for imperfections, as a part of the crafting process, and sometimes even by mistake. But one Lunarian's trash is another's treasure: these shards cast off by the upper class are the largest many Lunarians can afford.
title: Chipped Moonstone #1
